3","tid":1431604,"uid":281584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:57:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港，時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"63e20021dc107252a468c23a3d8a5b50afd8fc84","tid":1431604,"uid":302358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:57:54.000Z","msg":"欲加之罪，何患無詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"901d02b7fbfa4682eb5fa04ff0bfd2653bdd053f","tid":1431604,"uid":301218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:58:39.000Z","msg":"你support咪叫，唔support咪唔叫，起碼遊行我聽到時唔係個個都會跟住叫哩句，講左無大台，總之五大訴求係我地既終極目標，其他野兄弟爬山。"},{"pid":"207db207435e824293c800a5449590203d4d8b54","tid":1431604,"uid":36321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:00:01.000Z","msg":"成日都自閹<br />\n比比鳥叫人投票俾人屌港獨呀<br />\n5大訴求有雙普對中共都可以係港獨架<br />\n然後又驚激嬲中共啦播？<br />\n然後你係唔係自己閹埋佢唔講雙普變4大訴求呀？"},{"pid":"f48c0b34f07ea2f95b5f3ebef49f9723ba1013c5","tid":1431604,"uid":248290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:01:40.000Z","msg":"光復香港。守護家園<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9577e8a0451eb4641bd2094d8f600f806cfe41c","tid":1431604,"uid":221809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:05:21.000Z","msg":"根本冇需要改"},{"pid":"11ba3a435e52d892df3daae4e8da081d3832d87a","tid":1431604,"uid":106983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:25:37.000Z","msg":"或者我冇表達好自己想法<br />\n我冇意思要自閹訴求<br />\n我出發點只係希望將訴求合理化<br />\n令今次運動可以贏到最多野返黎<br />\n<br />\n亦可能係我意志唔夠硬淨 <br />\n先會咁諗<br />\n<br />\n此post已完"}]}